snippet.title: OXIDE Room 104 - ANNOUNCEMENT TEASER TRAILER
snippet.description:
OXIDE Room 104 is a psychological horror game. Your actions will decide the fate of this experience of classic horror inspired by Silent Hill and The Human Centipede.

"You are all my children now..."

#horrorgame #survivalhorror #unrealengine #PlayStation #Xbox #NintendoSwitch #Steam
